You walk over to the training grounds and look around to find a suitable spot to start stretching. It's been a while since you've managed to catch a moment alone to train, and you want to make every moment count.

As you look around the area, you notice a familiar figure sitting alone on the bleachers with a cigarette between his fingers. It's Rosinante, and as you look at him more closely, he seems to be deep in thought.

do show_character(rosinante, center, show)
