:: Part_1A

`name`: Commander, good afternoon! Is everything all right? You seem like you have a lot on your mind.
Rosinante: Hello, `name`! I didn't expect to see you here today.
Rosinante: All is well! I'm just figuring out some last minute details for the mission I'm going on later.
`name`: You're going on a mission later? But you seem so relaxed.
`name`: I'm often so nervous the day I have to go out in the field.
Rosinante: Ah, I remember going through that when I was a recruit.
Rosinante: After a while, you get used to it, you know? It's just a bit more complicated now since it wasn't originally my mission. I'm just filling in for Lieutenant Gray.
- Oh! Do you need any help? We could figure out a plan together. => Part_2A
- Are you going by yourself? => Part_2B
- That sounds like important work. I won't bother you anymore, Commander. => Part_1C

:: Part_2A

Rosinante: There's no need. I'm already in a hurry, but I just wanted to figure out some last minute details. I'll be good. I always work better when I'm already in action, anyway.
